summary: A subliminal OG. An extremely abbstract poem that may have gone too beserk...
poemContent:
A visaged wasteland,
hanging bodies, drops guts.
The raiskaus metsään,
in a kingdom of sus.

The first dutchess,
sussy grass,
ozymandias, invisioned, struck killed,
euthanasia,
fast.

Caesura. Azure urea,
fecal matter in a focal view.
Excrement litters North Korea.
Griffith did nothing wrong,
what about you?
